node.text: Come shopping at @IKEA with us! #ad We’re so excited to be a part of the first-ever, 24-hour #IKEAFestival: a celebration of life at home featuring musicians, chefs and creators from all over the world. We went to @IKEAUSA to explore home inspiration for the boys’ rooms for our upcoming move 😍 Which items are your favorite?... also, why was Westin so angry? 😂 To watch our shopping trip and so much more, check out IKEA.us/Festival!

node.text: I know a lot of us have questions about the COVID-19 vaccine. So when Desmond and I were presented with an opportunity to interview a doctor about it we were all in! Health and medical decisions is a personal decision for each family, so it is great to be informed. Tune in to see what Dr. Ross has to say about the vaccine and getting back to normal. #HealthyTexas #ad

node.text: I’ve always been so passionate about morning routines and starting your day on the right foot, while implementing healthy habits ✨ @FourSigmatic Plant-based Protein has some of the world’s most wonderful ingredients including pure plant protein, functional mushrooms, and adaptogens, and makes the best smoothies, shakes and pancakes. It doesn’t have any grains, gums, or other fillers and every single batch is rigorously lab tested for pesticides and heavy metals. It tastes sooo good 😍 No chalky aftertaste at all! My favorite is Sweet Vanilla, which uses the realest organic vanilla, not artificial flavors, stevia, or sweeteners. It’s seriously so good!! #ad #foursigmatic #magicmorningmoments

node.text: Come shopping at @IKEA with us! #ad We’re so excited to be a part of the first-ever, 24-hour #IKEAFestival: a celebration of life at home featuring musicians, chefs and creators from all over the world.
